<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rangriti - Page Not Found</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@400;700&family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            background-color: #f5e8d0; /* Sandalwood beige */
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(#e8d1b0 1px, transparent 1px),
                radial-gradient(#e8d1b0 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 40px 40px;
            background-position: 0 0, 20px 20px;
            color: #5c3e2a; /* Deep earthy brown */
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        /* Ethnic border pattern */
        .container::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            top: 20px;
            left: 20px;
            right: 20px;
            bottom: 20px;
            border: 2px solid #c19a6b; /* Warm bronze */
            border-image: 
                repeating-linear-gradient(
                    45deg,
                    #c19a6b,
                    #c19a6b 10px,
                    #e8d1b0 10px,
                    #e8d1b0 20px
                ) 10;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        .mandala {
            position: absolute;
            width: 400px;
            height: 400px;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle, #e8d1b0 10%, transparent 10%),
                radial-gradient(circle, #e8d1b0 20%, transparent 20%),
                radial-gradient(circle, #e8d1b0 30%, transparent 30%),
                radial-gradient(circle, #e8d1b0 40%, transparent 40%);
            background-size: 100px 100px;
            background-position: 0 0, 50px 50px, 0 100px, 100px 50px;
            opacity: 0.3;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .mandala:nth-child(1) {
            top: -150px;
            left: -150px;
            transform: rotate(15deg);
        }

        .mandala:nth-child(2) {
            bottom: -150px;
            right: -150px;
            transform: rotate(-15deg);
        }

        .error-code {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 12rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #8b5a2b; /* Rich bronze */
            text-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #d4b483, 8px 8px 0 rgba(139, 90, 43, 0.2);
            margin: 20px 0;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .error-code::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 10px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            width: 200px;
            height: 8px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, #b8860b, transparent);
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #5c3e2a;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .home-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #8b5a2b; /* Rich bronze */
            color: #f5e8d0;
            font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 0;
            margin-top: 20px;
            position: relative;
            border: 2px solid #5c3e2a;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(92, 62, 42, 0.2);
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        /* Handwoven button effect */
        .home-button::before,
        .home-button::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            background: #d4b483; /* Light sandalwood */
            width: 8px;
            height: 100%;
            top: 0;
        }

        .home-button::before {
            left: -10px;
            transform: skewY(-45deg);
        }

        .home-button::after {
            right: -10px;
            transform: skewY(45deg);
        }

        .home-button:hover {
            background: #9c6b3b;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(92, 62, 42, 0.3);
        }

        .home-button:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        /* Block print patterns */
        .pattern {
            position: absolute;
            opacity: 0.2;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .pattern-1 {
            top: 10%;
            left: 10%;
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background-image: 
                linear-gradient(45deg, #5c3e2a 25%, transparent 25%),
                linear-gradient(-45deg, #5c3e2a 25%, transparent 25%),
                linear-gradient(45deg, transparent 75%, #5c3e2a 75%),
                linear-gradient(-45deg, transparent 75%, #5c3e2a 75%);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            background-position: 0 0, 0 10px, 10px -10px, -10px 0px;
        }

        .pattern-2 {
            bottom: 15%;
            right: 15%;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle, #5c3e2a 30%, transparent 30%),
                radial-gradient(circle, #5c3e2a 30%, transparent 30%);
            background-size: 20px 20px;
            background-position: 0 0, 10px 10px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .error-code {
                font-size: 8rem;
            }
            
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5rem;
            }
            
            p {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
            
            .mandala {
                width: 250px;
                height: 250px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Decorative mandalas -->
    <div class="mandala"></div>
    <div class="mandala"></div>
    
    <!-- Ethnic patterns -->
    <div class="pattern pattern-1"></div>
    <div class="pattern pattern-2"></div>
    
    <div class="container">
        <div class="error-code">404</div>
        <h1>Oops! Something Went Wrong</h1>
        <p>It seems the page you're seeking has wandered off like a colorful kite in the monsoon breeze. Not to worry, let's guide you back to familiar ground. Try logging in to view the page.</p>
        <a href="/index.html" class="home-button">Return to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>